712	/**
713	 * When used inside a [`$derived`](https://svelte.dev/docs/svelte/$derived) or [`$effect`](https://svelte.dev/docs/svelte/$effect),
714	 * any state read inside `fn` will not be treated as a dependency.
715	 *
716	 * ```ts
717	 * $effect(() => {
718	 *   // this will run when `data` changes, but not when `time` changes
719	 *   save(data, {
720	 *     timestamp: untrack(() => time)
721	 *   });
722	 * });
